Move one week to right, and change window size to 2 or 4 weeks.
Today is not fixed to the rightmost side.

In `AttributeDetailActivity` toolbar, a cancel button is out of position.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26426778/34349405-386263ca-ea54-11e7-8a5e-ac01031021f8.png)

title: Visibility problem of connection indicator
body:
When user removes a connection in `AttributeDetailActivity` and saves changes, Change is not immediately applied to connectionIndicatorSubProxy in `TrackerDetailStructureTabFragment`.
I think this problem is occurred by inflated view from ViewStub.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26426778/34349627-8c32bfa8-ea55-11e7-9833-4bf008f7bdde.png)

title: Enable external service connections directly from the services tab
body:
This PR allows not only a method of adding external service in `AttributeDetailActivity` but also selecting the attribute to be connected from `ServiceListFragment`. 
 If there are not any valid trackers or attributes yet, user can add a new tracker or a new attribute to attach to the tracker.

title: Connect Preference with AppUpdater
body:
This PR connects preference that checks newly update version with `AppUpdater`.
It also adds a new user permission (REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKAGES) to resolve a problem in specific android versions(Android API 24+).
